data.name: ReadCsePerson
data.value: select top(1) NUMB from CKT_CSE_PERSON where NUMB = @numb

data.name: ReadEmployment1
data.value: select distinct T1.IDENTIFIER, T1.TYPE, T1.LAST_QTR_INCOME, T1.LAST_QTR, T1.LAST_QTR_YR, T1.SECOND_QTR_INCOME, T1.SECOND_QTR, T1.SECOND_QTR_YR, T1.THIRD_QTR_INCOME, T1.THIRD_QTR, T1.THIRD_QTR_YR, T1.FOURTH_QTR_INCOME, T1.FOURTH_QTR, T1.FOURTH_QTR_YR, T1.SENT_DT, T1.RETURN_DT, T1.RETURN_CD, T1.LAST_UPDATED_TMST, T1.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T1.CSP_I_NUMBER, T1.EMP_ID, T1.WORKER_ID, T1.START_DT, T1.END_DT from CKT_EMPLOYER T2 join CKT_INCOME_SOURCE T1 on (@cspINumber = T1.CSP_I_NUMBER) and (T2.IDENTIFIER = T1.EMP_ID) and (T2.EIN = @ein) order by T1.END_DT desc, T1.IDENTIFIER desc

data.name: ReadEmployment2
data.value: select distinct T1.IDENTIFIER, T1.TYPE, T1.LAST_QTR_INCOME, T1.LAST_QTR, T1.LAST_QTR_YR, T1.SECOND_QTR_INCOME, T1.SECOND_QTR, T1.SECOND_QTR_YR, T1.THIRD_QTR_INCOME, T1.THIRD_QTR, T1.THIRD_QTR_YR, T1.FOURTH_QTR_INCOME, T1.FOURTH_QTR, T1.FOURTH_QTR_YR, T1.SENT_DT, T1.RETURN_DT, T1.RETURN_CD, T1.NAME, T1.LAST_UPDATED_TMST, T1.LAST_UPDATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TIMESTAMP, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CSP_I_NUMBER, T1.SELF_EMPLOYED_IND, T1.EMP_ID, T1.SEND_TO, T1.WORKER_ID, T1.START_DT, T1.END_DT, T1.NOTE, T1.NOTE_2 from CKT_EMPLOYER T2 join CKT_INCOME_SOURCE T1 on (@cspINumber = T1.CSP_I_NUMBER) and (T2.IDENTIFIER = T1.EMP_ID) and (T2.EIN = @ein) and (T1.END_DT = @endDt) order by T1.END_DT, T1.IDENTIFIER desc

data.name: ReadInvalidSsn
data.value: select top(1) CSP_NUMBER, SSN from CKT_INVALID_SSN where (@cspNumber = CSP_NUMBER) and (SSN = @ssn)

data.name: ReadLegalActionIncomeSource
data.value: select distinct T1.CSP_NUMBER, T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER, T1.ISR_IDENTIFIER, T1.EFFECTIVE_DT, T1.CREATED_BY, T1.CREATED_TSTAMP, T1.WITHHOLDING_TYPE, T1.END_DT, T1.WAGE_OR_NON_WAGE, T1.ORDER_TYPE, T1.IDENTIFIER from CKT_LEGAL_ACTION T2 join CKT_LEGAL_ACT_ISRC T1 on (@cspNumber = T1.CSP_NUMBER) and (@isrIdentifier = T1.ISR_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.LEGAL_ACTION_ID = T1.LGA_IDENTIFIER) and (T2.CLASSIFICATION = 'I') and (T2.ACTION_TAKEN = 'ORDIWO2') order by T1.CREATED_TSTAMP desc

data.name: ReadMilitary
data.value: select distinct T1.IDENTIFIER, T1.TYPE, T1.RETURN_DT, T1.RETURN_CD, T1.CSP_I_NUMBER, T1.EMP_ID, T1.START_DT, T1.END_DT from CKT_EMPLOYER T2 join CKT_INCOME_SOURCE T1 on (@cspINumber = T1.CSP_I_NUMBER) and (T2.IDENTIFIER = T1.EMP_ID) and (T2.EIN = @ein) order by T1.END_DT desc, T1.IDENTIFIER desc
